        "subject": "LU-139 move DCACHE_LUSTRE_INVALID to higher bit to prevent conflict with other dentry flags",
        "message": "LU-139 move DCACHE_LUSTRE_INVALID to higher bit to prevent conflict with other dentry flags\n\n2.6.38 comes with a bunch of new dentry flags and one of them\n(i.e. DCACHE_OP_REVALIDATE) conflicts with our DCACHE_LUSTRE_INVALID.\n\nChange-Id: I11de689058d12b07b2f00191f2d175d48a90ff8e\nSigned-off-by: Johann Lombardi <johann@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
